originalText.text:
Update spring 2021. It's been quiet. Surprised at the support I'm receiving. The new recreation person is very personable, my son likes talking to her. He's more comfortable walking around the building and calling staff for me. West 116 store front  has been a great support helping me with documents that I need printed. No more drama and haven't seen new staff members in a while so that's a plus for me.  I like consistently,  if I ask I get an answer and I'm not hearing anymore gossip.

I just wish they would help those with substance abuse problems. The smell from the burning drugs is very annoying,  I found a .... haphazardly thrown in the trash. If they could get help from the supportive housing people to get those people off or get them the help they need outside of this building.  I don't want my son smelling that multiple times everyday.  4 stars
